<p>Cloud</p>

<p>Cloud technology is a method of delivering computing services over the internet. It provides users with on-demand access to a shared pool of configurable computing resources, such as servers, storage, and applications. Cloud technology offers businesses a flexible and cost-effective solution for managing their IT infrastructure.</p>
Features:
<ul>
    <li>Scalability</li>
    <li>Flexibility</li>
    <li>Cost-effectiveness</li>
    <li>High Availability</li>
    <li>Automatic Software Updates</li>
    <li>Disaster Recovery</li>
    <li>Security</li>
</ul>